Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.24,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Esta é uma batalha real entre esses guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:16.45,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,É hora do gongo inicial!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.33,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Agora então...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.69,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Cavendish-sama!
