Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.60,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Morra, Rebeca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.46,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Espero que você esteja vendo isso, Soldier-san.
