Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.76,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Os esquadrões Yellow Kabu e Pink Bee chegaram de Green Bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.86,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho, Leão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.33,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Chegou a hora, capitão.
